										<span>Professional video editing with cinematic effects</span>
									</div>
									<div class="service-item">
										<span class="service-icon">ðŸŽ¨</span>
										<span>Custom digital illustrations and artwork</span>
									</div>
									<div class="service-item">
										<span class="service-icon">ðŸŽ­</span>
										<span>2D/3D animation for characters and scenes</span>
									</div>
									<div class="service-item">
										<span class="service-icon">ðŸ’¼</span>
										<span>Portfolio-ready visuals for creators & small brands</span>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<!-- Process -->
						<div class="about-card process-card">
							<div class="card-header">
								<h2>How I Work</h2>
								<div class="card-accent"></div>
							</div>
							<div class="card-content">
								<p class="process-intro">
									Every project begins with your idea. I understand the mood, style, and emotion you want, then turn it into a polished visual using a structured process:
								</p>
								<div class="process-steps">
									<div class="process-step">
										<div class="step-number">1</div>
										<div class="step-content">
											<h4>Concept Discussion</h4>
											<p>We talk about your vision and requirements</p>
										</div>
									</div>
									<div class="process-step">
										<div class="step-number">2</div>
										<div class="step-content">
											<h4>Rough Sketch / Layout</h4>
											<p>Initial concepts and planning</p>
										</div>
									</div>
									<div class="process-step">
										<div class="step-number">3</div>
										<div class="step-content">
											<h4>Line Art & Details</h4>
											<p>Refining the artwork structure</p>
										</div>
									</div>
									<div class="process-step">
										<div class="step-number">4</div>
										<div class="step-content">
											<h4>Coloring or Editing</h4>
											<p>Adding life and final touches</p>
										</div>
									</div>
									<div class="process-step">
										<div class="step-number">5</div>
										<div class="step-content">
